name: Roghni Paratha Recipe | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Roghni Paratha Recipe: White Flour 1/2 kg Oil 4 tbsp Salt 1/2 tsp 1 Egg Baking Soda 1/4 ts Ghee for fying
instructions: In a bowl, add all ingredients except ghee and Mix. Now Kneading well, and make medium balls. Heat ghee and fry. Roghni Paratha is ready.
